726778f.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - 73rd Street
726778f.text:
Grand Avenue, north side, between 73rd Street and 74th
Street, showing the Jeronus Rapelje house. Louis B. Myers,
a plasterer was the occupant in 1924. The brick buildings
adjoining the white house are the property of William Wolf.
January 1924.
Eumene L. Armbruster Collection
